Package: Friedman
Title: Simple Data Visualization and Analysis Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kyla", "Garcia", email = "kyla.garcia@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The Friedman package provides simple and intuitive functions 
    for cleaning, summarizing, and visualizing datasets. It is designed 
    for students and beginner R users who want to explore data quickly 
    using streamlined functions built on ggplot2 and dplyr.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
